To exit &edvi, use your mouse to select the
.keyword File
menu, and pick the
.keyword Exit
item.
If you do not have a mouse, press
.param ALT_F
(hold down the
.param ALT
key and press the letter F)
and use the down arrow key to highlight the
.keyword Exit
item. Pressing the
.param ENTER
key selects the
.keyword Exit
item.
